resource: 1002706.derived=false 1002706.source=MANUAL_IMPORT 1002706.vtc=true 1002706.description=Toyota strives to build vehicles to match customer interest and thus they typically are built with popular options and option packages. Not all options/packages are available separately and some may not be available in all regions of the country. If you would prefer a vehicle with no or different options, contact your dealer to check for current availability or the possibility of placing a special order.
